# '''Public Key''': An address where ''VOTEs'' will be sent if identity is validated by peers. This will be the Decentralized Identifier (DID) pointing to this user. If this identity eventually is voted as corrupted or the user (or any listed witnesses) revoke it, then the allocated ''VOTEs'' will get invalidated for future use.

